      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Get ready for your next adventure with this dependable ride! While it shows some honest wear and tear from its time on the road, it remains a solid and functional vehicle that's ready to get you where you need to go. It's in fair condition and perfect for someone looking for a reliable, budget-friendly option with plenty of life left in it!",
