      "description": "This vehicle represents the pinnacle of automotive preservation. Maintained to an exacting standard, it remains in pristine condition, offering an experience indistinguishable from its original showroom debut. Every detail, from the flawless exterior finish to the untouched interior upholstery, reflects a history of meticulous care. For the discerning collector who demands nothing less than perfection, this offering stands as a rare opportunity to acquire a benchmark specimen.",
      "price": 48500.0,
